RATANDA police in Heidelberg, Ekurhuleni, are looking for this man.The man allegedly stabbed another man to death in phase two, Obed Nkosi on Thursday evening. Cops were called to the scene and found the body of the 30-year-old victim lying in a pool of blood.Police spokesman Constable Xolani Mkhize said the victim had multiple stab wounds to his upper body.&ldquo;Community members are advised not to approach the suspect because he is considered to be dangerous.&ldquo;Those with information are asked to call Ratanda police on 016 343 6022 or contact their nearest police station,&rdquo; said Mkhize.